比其竞争对手的可折叠产品 Pixel Fold 厚。）</p><p>我收集了三星的其他<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/summer-samsung-unpacked-2023-everything-announced-at-the-event-134721886.html"><ins>亮点</ins></a>——今年你会购买可折叠手机吗？</p><p> ——马特·史密斯</p><p><em>​​您可以每天将这些报告直接发送到您的收件箱。</em><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>在这里订阅！</em></a></p><p></p><h3>三星 2023 年 7 月亮点揭晓</h3><p><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-z-flip-5-hands-on-a-larger-external-display-holds-promise-110059050.html"><ins>三星 Galaxy Z Flip 5 上手：更大的外接显示屏有望实现</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-5-hands-on-specs-price-is-samsung-squandering-its-head-start-110009600.html"><ins>三星 Galaxy Z Fold 5 上手体验：三星正在浪费领先优势吗？</ins></a></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-z-flip-5-vs-moto-razr-a-clamshell-comparison-114506038.html"><ins>Galaxy Z Flip 5 与 Moto Razr+：翻盖式比较</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-galaxy-z-fold-5-vs-pixel-fold-did-samsung-rise-to-googles-challenge-113709671.html"><ins>Galaxy Z Fold 5 vs Pixel Fold：三星能否应对谷歌的挑战？</ins></a></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-6-hands-on-the-spinning-bezels-triumphant-return-110047694.html"><ins>三星 Galaxy Watch 6 上手体验：旋转表圈凯旋归来</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s9-ultra-hands-on-a-premium-tablet-with-water-protection-110020872.html"><ins>三星 Galaxy Tab S9 Ultra 上手体验：具有防水功能的优质平板电脑</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-5-pre-orders-on-amazon-include-a-200-gift-card-142351976.html"><ins>亚马逊预购三星 Galaxy Z Fold 5 含价值 200 美元的礼品卡</ins></a></p><p></p><h3>您可能错过的其他重要故事</h3><p><a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-9995-fuell-fllow-electric-motorcycle-is-available-for-pre-order-today-220016821.html"><ins>售价 9,995 美元的 Fuell Fllow 电动摩托车今天即可接受预订</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/augusts-playstation-plus-monthly-games-include-deaths-door-and-dreams-182331045.html"><ins>8 月的 PlayStation Plus 月度游戏包括《死亡之门》和《梦想》</ins></a></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/xbox-home-screen-revamp-provides-quicker-access-to-games-173010398.html"><ins>Xbox 主屏幕改造可让您更快地访问游戏</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-headphones-150030794.html"><ins>2023 年最佳无线耳机</ins></a></p><p></p><h2><a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-had-its-best-quarter-since-2021-despite-losing-more-money-on-the-metaverse-231925266.html">尽管 Metaverse 亏损更多，但 Meta 仍录得自 2021 年以来最好的季度业绩</a></h2><h3>Meta“完全致力于”Metaverse。</h3><h3></h3><p> Meta 刚刚经历了 2021 年以来最好的季度，尽管它在 Metaverse 上继续亏损大量资金。事实上，该公司表示，预计未来一年的努力将损失更多资金。我的意思是，公司改名了——它不会那么轻易放弃。</p><p>根据该公司最新的财报，负责监管虚拟和增强现实项目的 Meta 部门 Reality Labs 在 2023 年第二季度亏损了 37 亿美元，收入仅为 2.76 亿美元。除了 Metaverse 之外，Meta 在本季度表现强劲，营收为 320 亿美元，比去年增长 11%。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-had-its-best-quarter-since-2021-despite-losing-more-money-on-the-metaverse-231925266.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-members-can-now-get-pre-approved-for-new-boost-infinite-plans-120058552.html">Amazon Prime 会员现在可以获得新的 Boost Infinite 蜂窝计划的预先批准</a></h2><h3>有一家店面出售 Boost Infinite 的 SIM 套件。</h3><h3></h3><p>亚马逊与 Dish Wireless 旗下的无线运营商 Boost Infinite 合作，并推出了一个店面，让后者的 SIM 套件更容易使用。虽然亚马逊销售来自多家提供商的 SIM 卡，但这是一次真正的合作，可以自动为 Prime 会员提供该运营商每月 25 美元后付费无线套餐的资格预审。订户可以从亚马逊商店购买 Boost Infinite 的 Unlimited 25 美元 SIM 套件，享受 20% 的折扣。这并不完全是我们听说过的<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-is-reportedly-trying-to-offer-prime-subscribers-free-cell-phone-service-140026387.html"><ins>免费手机服务</ins></a>传闻，但折扣就是折扣……</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-members-can-now-get-pre-approved-for-new-boost-infinite-plans-120058552.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-tells-advertisers-to-spend-1000-per-month-or-risk-losing-verification-status-201528621.html">X 威胁要取消每月支出低于 1,000 美元的广告商的验证状态</a></h2><h3>马斯克表示，这是为了防止诈骗者创建数百万个帐户。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/x-tells-advertisers-to-spend-1000-per-month-or-risk-losing-verification-status-201528621.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/bebf05a0-2c5b-11ee-99bf-5ba24ad614dc" style="height:450px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="85caf38b-9dc8-34ad-a03b-b420d9fa0ddd"><figcaption></figcaption> <div class="photo-credit">Engadget</div></figure></a><p>据报道，Twitter（现在的 X）正在向广告商施加强硬措施，以提高其利润。本月早些时候的报告显示，X 的收入下降了 50%，令人震惊。据<em>《华尔街日报》报道</em>，该公司的最新策略是要求品牌每月至少花费 1,000 美元用于广告，以维持其在平台上的验证状态。马斯克表示，“较高”的成本是一种预防措施，有助于减少在该平台上创建“数百万个账户”的诈骗者数量。百万！</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-tells-advertisers-to-spend-1000-per-month-or-risk-losing-verification-status-201528621.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-everything-announced-at-samsungs-summer-unpacked-2023-event-111543940.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-everything-announced-at-samsungs-summer-unpacked-2023-event-111543940.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 857a285e-8288-48ba-b124-48f6e5042ab4</guid><dc:creator>马特·史密斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jul 2023 11:15:43 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690453194</ingested><modified> 2023-07-27T10:19:59+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></categor